# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:53
msgid "Built-in Tutorial"
msgstr "Innebygd veiledning"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:54
msgid ""
"When you first launch OpenShot, you will be presented with a friendly built-"
"in tutorial. It will demonstrate and explain the basics. Clicking :guilabel:"
"`Next` will jump to the next topic. You can always view this tutorial again "
"from the :guilabel:`Help→Tutorial` menu."
